{"tid":2414553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賀歲大片 》央視熱烈恭賀中印邊界犧牲官兵成為英雄","createTime":"2021-02-19T13:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T12:21:53.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78a2bc366c3046c429c5f5c653311461387be858","tid":2414553,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:12:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">這段視頻，還原了喀喇崑崙那場英勇戰鬥&hellip;&hellip;</span></strong><br />\n來源：央視軍事<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-19 19:52<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gHQMMiNO3Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgHQMMiNO3Bo&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=2be46c83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gHQMMiNO3Bo</a><br />\n<br />\n祖國西部邊陲，喀喇崑崙高原。去年6月，外軍公然違背與我方達成的共識，悍然越線挑釁。在前出交涉和激烈鬥爭中，團長祁發寶身先士卒，身負重傷；營長陳紅軍、戰士陳祥榕突入重圍營救，奮力反擊，英勇犧牲；戰士肖思遠，突圍後義無反顧返回營救戰友，戰鬥至生命最後一刻；戰士王焯冉，在渡河前出支援途中，拼力救助被沖散的戰友脫險，自己卻淹沒在冰河之中。<span class=\"red\">中央軍委授予祁發寶&ldquo;衛國戍邊英雄團長&rdquo;榮譽稱號，追授陳紅軍&ldquo;衛國戍邊英雄&rdquo;榮譽稱號，給陳祥榕、肖思遠、王焯冉追記一等功。</span>英雄雖已離去，精神永駐邊關！ （記者李波 張天宇 李一楠 董豫 楊鵬 郭帥 康樂 湯健寧 羅楊 胡永波 鄭強龍 王建軍）<br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：張燕萍"},{"pid":"b8ba076e7f472dac95b0677b3f2471bacc790afc","tid":2414553,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N-MJgDvxlQ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN-MJgDvxlQ0&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=6cb5172e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N-MJgDvxlQ0</a>"},{"pid":"6de20e7fd9568eb60f9f5b607f201aa8eada5d46","tid":2414553,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JG0Xd_joSuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJG0Xd_joSuo&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=0cc023c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JG0Xd_joSuo</a>"